8 kyu 
Easy SQL: Square Root and Log

SELECT SQRT(number1) AS root, LOG(number2) AS log
FROM decimals;
-----------------------------------

-----------------------------------
8 kyu
Easy SQL: Rounding Decimals

SELECT FLOOR(number1) AS number1, CEILING(number2) AS number2
FROM decimals;
