SQL Basics: Simple MIN / MAX

SELECT MAX(age) AS age_max, MIN(age) AS age_min
FROM people;
-----------------------------------

-----------------------------------
8 kyu
SQL Basics: Simple WHERE and ORDER BY

SELECT * 
FROM people
WHERE age > 50
ORDER BY age DESC;
-----------------------------------

-----------------------------------
8 kyu
Easy SQL - Ordering

SELECT * 
FROM companies
ORDER BY employees DESC;
